Package: gtsummaryAddin
Type: Package
Title: Adds interactive add-in of gtsummary to Rstudio
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Norimitsu","Nishida", email="ma06063@gmail.com", role=c("aut","cre"))
Description: Adds interactive add-in of gtsummary to Rstudio.
    This package provides an interactive GUI of the gtsummary package.
    The gtsummary is a package for making a sophisticated table from R
    objects using the gt package. This package loads a shiny app for
    call tbl_summary and tbl_regression function from gtsummary.
    This package only borrows a part of the powerful gtsummary package.
    For utilizing the full functionality of the gtsummary, users 
    recommended hard code the R script.
BugReports: https://github.com/ironwest/gtsummary_addin/issues
